    <briefdescription>
<para>Console Program - Shell-like terminal interface for debugging and system control. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a bash/sh-like terminal interface with command history, output display, and command execution. Features include:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para><ref refid="classCommand" kindref="compound">Command</ref> history navigation (up/down arrows)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="classCommand" kindref="compound">Command</ref> output display</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Scrollable terminal view</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="classCommand" kindref="compound">Command</ref> echoing with prompts </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
